      "text": [
        " «لِيُعِدْ كُلَّ صَلاَةٍ صَلاَّهَا خَلْفَهُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1116 - It was narrated from Isma'il ibn Muslim that he asked Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) about praying behind a man who denies (or rejects) the decree (Qadar) of Allah (swt), the Mighty and Majestic.\nHe (Al-Sadiq) replied: \"He should repeat every prayer he performed behind him”."
        ]
      }
